race.comment: HEY ARTIE (1) has mixed form a little and missed the frame the last two but was a Maiden winner three back (19.82) at this track over 352m. Key player on best and worth another chance. SHIAN MIKEY (2) ran above expectations last time to win his first race by 0.8 lengths at Capalaba over 366m (20.09). Boxed well here. Has placed one times at this trip. Should be in this for a long way. ELITE ENERGY (8) placed last time and cannot be ignored. Something for the Multiples: CANYA JELLY BEAN (5)
